## Limitations
This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the scope of the sources reviewed. Some sources may not reflect the most current technological advancements or policy changes in the manufacturing sector. Additionally, the report primarily focuses on the U.S. and European contexts, which may not fully represent global manufacturing practices and their environmental impacts.

